channel.title: Commands aren't working
channel.description: The only commands I have that work are the ones that were originally in my client, and I'm using Phonescape V2.0 as my source. I added in my commands, showed them to Sven and she fixed one, but it didn't work, and I thought it was a problem with my Compiler, so I reinstalled everything, and my compiler worked, I get on, but the commands still don't work, help please? Also, on the Runserver thing, when it shows the commands I typed, no errors show up, it'll just say like teh crafterz-playercommand:archer or something, no errors though. :(
